{
    "version": "1.5.1",
    "description": "一款采用 WinUI 3 框架打造的尖端优化器，旨在提升 Windows 设备的性能 | A cutting-edge optimizer built with the WinUI 3 framework, designed to amplify the performance of Windows devices.",
    "homepage": "https://rayenghanmi.github.io/rytunex",
    "license": {
        "identifier": "AGPL-3.0-only",
